'''词根'''（root，root word）又称'''语根'''、'''根词'''<ref>https://www.termonline.cn/word/121899/1#</ref>，是基本构词的基本[[語素|词素]]，与词缀相对并携带主要词汇信息。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://linguistics.stonybrook.edu/_pdf/dissertation/Volpe_2005_dissertation.pdf|title=Japanese Morphology and Its Theoretical Consequences: Derivational Morphology in Distributed Morphology|author=Mark Joseph Volpe|date=2005年12月|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210116033554/https://linguistics.stonybrook.edu/_pdf/dissertation/Volpe_2005_dissertation.pdf|archivedate=2021|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://babel.ucsc.edu/~hank/mrg.readings/Siddiqi_Diss.pdf|title=On a Theory of Root Allomorphy|author=Daniel Siddiqi|date=2006|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210702014739/https://babel.ucsc.edu/~hank/mrg.readings/Siddiqi_Diss.pdf|archivedate=2021|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://udel.edu/~dlarsen/ling101/slides/Morphology.pdf|title=Morphology|author=Darrell Larsen|publisher=University of Delaware|date=2012|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210702013847/http://udel.edu/~dlarsen/ling101/slides/Morphology.pdf|archivedate=2021|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.oakton.edu/user/3/gherrera/Greek%20and%20Latin%20Roots%20in%20English/greek_and_latin_roots.pdf|title=List of Greek and Latin roots in English|author=Gerardo Herrera|date=2012|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210426070219/https://www.oakton.edu/user/3/gherrera/Greek%20and%20Latin%20Roots%20in%20English/greek_and_latin_roots.pdf|archivedate=2021|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.soas.ac.uk/linguistics/research/workingpapers/volume-14/file37818.pdf|title=On synthesis, fusion and the difference between them|author=László Kristó|publisher=SOAS Working Papers in Linguistics (Vol. 14 (2006): 63-94)|date=2006|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190808104844/https://www.soas.ac.uk/linguistics/research/workingpapers/volume-14/file37818.pdf|archivedate=2021|deadurl=no}}</ref>

词根有两种，能够独立构词的为'''自由词根'''（free root），必须与其他词素组合构词的是'''黏着词根'''（bound root）。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://clslearninglab.org/assets/english/English%20Grade%208.pdf|title=The English Language From Sound to Sense|author=Gerald Patrick Delahunty 、 James Jim Garvey|publisher=The WAC Clearinghouse 、 Parlor Press|date=2010|ISBN=9781602351806|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210702020302/http://clslearninglab.org/assets/english/English%20Grade%208.pdf|archivedate=2021|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://arts-sciences.buffalo.edu/content/dam/arts-sciences/linguistics/AlumniDissertations/Melinger%20dissertation.pdf|title=Morphological Complexity in English Prefixed Words: An Experimental Investigation|author=Alissa Melinger|date=2004|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210702022021/https://arts-sciences.buffalo.edu/content/dam/arts-sciences/linguistics/AlumniDissertations/Melinger%20dissertation.pdf|archivedate=2021|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://gawron.sdsu.edu/functions_of_language/course_core/lectures/word_structure.pdf|title=Word Structure|author=Jean Mark Gawron|publisher=San Diego State University|date=2013年1月|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210702022502/https://gawron.sdsu.edu/functions_of_language/course_core/lectures/word_structure.pdf|archivedate=2021|deadurl=no}}</ref>

==閃語系的詞根==
閃語系的詞根是各種語言中比較特別的一種，因為他們的詞根都由三個辅音组成。例如以下的[[希伯來語|希伯來語]]例子中：

:'''''gdl''''' 是所有表示“大”這個字的詞根，但不是詞語，也不包含任何時態。
:'''''g'''a'''d'''o'''l''''' 是“大”的陽性形容詞。
:'''''gd'''o'''l'''a'' 是“大”的陰性形容詞。
:'''''g'''i'''dd'''e'''l''''' 是“他在種植......”的[[及物動詞|及物動詞]]形式。
:'''''g'''a'''d'''a'''l''''' 是“他在種植”的[[不及物動詞|不及物動詞]]形式。
:''hi'''gd'''i'''l''''' 是“他在放大......”的[[及物動詞|及物動詞]]形式。
:''ma'''gd'''e'''l'''et'' 是“放大鏡”的意思（[[名詞|名詞]]）。

